      • byName

        public static Field byName(Class<? extends EventBuilder> eb,
                           String name)

        Get a field by name. It first looks up the common fields, and if none of them apply, creates a reflection-based field.

        Parameters:
        eb - The event builder.
        name - The field name. The name can be suffixed with “?” to make it optional.
        Returns:
        The field, or null if no such field can be defined.
